msgstr ""
"The Scrapper's ship is now torn to shreds and the Kestrel Miner hails you. \"That's fantastic, we always appreciate help! CHEEESE! BEAM THEM, uhhhhh... THE BLUEPRINTS FOR OUR SHIP! AND THAT GARBAGE WEAPON THAT LANCER MADE!\".\n"
"\t\t\tWhile searching through the wreckage of the ship, you find a wounded Trash Eater clutching an advanced Flak Cannon. You're familiar with how wounded scrappers will eat weapons to survive, but the Trash Eater just holds it, staring at you.\n"
"\t\t\tYou can offer him a position on your ship though it may cost you."

